Install Astronomy software on MAC


1.brew
/usr/bin/ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)"
general command
  brew search name # search package
  brew list # list the package that has been installed


2.sextractor
Download version 2.5 from here
./configure
make
sudo make install

3.macport
Could be download on the website
How to use
  check whether install or not: port
  search software name: port search name
  use port to install software:sudo port install name
   list the package that has been installed: port installed

4.How to set the environment
vim .bash_profile
path
/usr/local/Cellar/gcc/8.2.0/bin:/usr/local/Cellar/gcc/8.2.0/lib
origin：/anaconda3/bin:$PATH"
alias gcc='gcc-8'
alias g++='g++-8'
alias c++='c++-8'
Gcc -v check

服务器上安装anaconda3
1.官网上下载linux版本
2.上传至服务器，
3.bash AnacondaXXXXXX(之后全部yes
4.source ~/.bashrc
5.查看是否安装 conda --version
6.查看python环境

安装Jupiter notebook
1.jupyter notebook --generate-config（配置文件)
2.生成密码
$ipython
In [1]: from notebook.auth import passwd

In [2]: passwd()
Enter password:
Verify password:
Out[2]: 'sha1:cd723d3e4b0a:e5ca450bbedb63511c78989ea16b8d26941227fb'
3.修改配置文件
vim ~/.jupyter/jupyter_notebook_config.py 
4.添加/修改如下字段
c.NotebookApp.ip='*' #意思是任意IP都可以访问
c.NotebookApp.password = u'sha1:cd723d3e4b0a:e5ca450bbedb63511c78989ea16b8d26941227fb' #刚才那个生成的密文
c.NotebookApp.open_browser = False  #意思是默认不打开浏览器
c.NotebookApp.port =8888 #随便指定一个你想要的端口,后面可以从这个端口使用
5.启动Jupiter
Jupiter notebook --no-browser --port=10000
后台脚本修改


安装 iraf
参见http://research.iac.es/sieinvens/siepedia/pmwiki.php?n=HOWTOs.IrafMacOSX#IRAFsetup
快速安装iraf 大法，Quick and easy IRAF installation procedure for macOS (之前我一定是傻了才没有看到这个方法)
具体如下：
1.安装
cd ~/Downloads/ 
wget ftp://iraf.noao.edu/iraf/v216/PCIX/iraf.macx.x86_64.tar.gz
2.设置参数
First set up the IRAF home directory and run mkiraf. 
cd ~/ 
mkdir iraf ; cd iraf 
mkiraf (select xgterm as terminal type) 


xgterm & or 
xgterm -ls & 
(the latter will launch xgterm as a login shell, use it if you miss the settings or aliases defined in .bash_profile)
Check the login.cl file just created. If the cache variable is set to "/tmp" or "/tmp//", change it to something like "/tmp/cache/" or "/iraf/cache/".
3.运行
xgterm
cd ~/iraf/ 
ecl or c


安装ps2eps ----将pdf转化为eps
brew install ps2eps

添加命令到路径
运行
Echo $PATH
出现
/opt/local/bin:/opt/local/sbin:/usr/local/Cellar/gcc/8.2.0/bin:/anaconda3/bin:/anaconda3/condabin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin:/usr/sbin:/sbin:/Library/TeX/texbin:/opt/X11/bin
用:分割可以添加的路径
e.g.
mv xx /usr/local/bin

